<h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" id="brigitte">Brigitte</h2>

<h3 class="mb-1">Against</h3>
<span class="text-small mb-2 font-italic">Duels: Difficult | Teamfights: Decent</span>

<p class="mb-1">
  A straight up 1 versus one will be very difficult. Even a mediocre Brigitte will beat you without much trouble. The difficulty lies in trying to stun her. If she juggles her shield between swings she will never get stunned. Your best bet is trying to dodge the stun and sticking as close to her as you possibly can. If all goes well you will eventually stun her and be able to double headshot her and her constant healing will be no problem. Unfortunately this is an unlikely scenario. Her constant damage is shield will make it very difficult. <br>
  If the Brigitte comes running at you and never lifts her shield you can easily take her out before she can kill you, but any half decent Brigitte will not play like that.<br>
  <strong>To summarise; avoid dueling Brigitte.</strong>
</p>

